title: Caitlyn Jenner Is Now Legally a Woman: Judge Signs Off on Name and Gender Change
text: Bruce Jenner has legally been erased. A judge signed off on the petition to change the name and gender, from male to female, filed by Caitlyn Jenner , aka the world’s most famous trans-woman right now.
